title.rendered: DLF Privana West Sector 76 Gurgaon | DLF New Launch

content.rendered:
Introducing DLF Privana West: Your Gateway to Luxury Living in Gurgaon

For those seeking the epitome of luxury living in Gurgaon, look no further than DLF Privana West. Nestled in the prestigious Sector 76, this upcoming residential project by DLF Homes promises to redefine urban living with its exquisite design, world-class amenities, and unparalleled attention to detail.

Luxury Redefined:
DLF Privana West is more than just a residential project – it’s a lifestyle destination. Spread across a sprawling 12.57 acres, this RERA-registered housing society boasts 795 units housed within 5 towers, each standing tall with 41 floors of opulence. With possession slated for December 2028, DLF Privana West offers a variety of options to suit every budget, making it an ideal choice for homebuyers seeking the perfect blend of luxury and affordability.

Prime Location:
Situated in Sector 76, Gurgaon, DLF Privana West enjoys a prime location with easy access to key landmarks, amenities, and entertainment options. Surrounded by iconic luxury developments, prestigious international schools, upscale boutiques, and fine dining restaurants, residents will experience the convenience of urban living at its finest. Plus, with proximity to major highways and the Sector 55-56 Metro Station, commuting throughout Gurgaon and beyond is a breeze.

Must-Know Features:
DLF Privana West offers an array of amenities designed to enhance residents’ lifestyles. From CCTV camera security and 24×7 power backup to lush green spaces and recreational facilities, every aspect of this project has been carefully curated to cater to the needs of modern urban dwellers. S.R.S. Hospital and Critical Care Unit, a popular landmark in Sector 76, adds to the convenience of living in this vibrant neighbourhood.

Exclusive Brochure and Photos:
Want to learn more about DLF Privana West? Download the official brochure to get a comprehensive look at this upcoming housing society, including details on amenities, features, payment plans, and more. Plus, view interiors and exterior images of residential properties for sale to envision life at DLF Privana West in Sector 76.

Address and Locality Insights:
DLF Privana West is located in Sector 76, Gurgaon – a thriving neighbourhood ranked #5 in the Top 20 in Southern Peripheral Road. With an average rating of 3.6 out of 5 from existing residents, Sector 76 offers a desirable mix of urban amenities and natural beauty, making it an ideal destination for homebuyers seeking a serene yet connected lifestyle.

Exquisite Specifications:
Experience luxury at every turn with meticulously designed living spaces featuring imported marble flooring, acrylic emulsion walls, and modular wardrobes. The modern kitchen boasts granite countertops, CP fittings, and high-end appliances, while the serene bathrooms feature marble floors, glass shower partitions, and premium sanitary ware.

Safety and Security:
DLF Privana West prioritizes resident safety with a range of security features, including secured gated entrances, CCTV surveillance, and access control systems. Plus, with a focus on eco-friendly living, the project incorporates rainwater harvesting systems and treated water from STP for flushing and horticulture.

Experience Elevated Living:
With its prime location, luxurious amenities, and impeccable design, DLF Privana West offers residents the ultimate urban living experience in Gurgaon. Whether you’re seeking a spacious family home or an exclusive penthouse retreat, this project has something for everyone. Don’t miss your chance to elevate your lifestyle – explore DLF Privana West today!

Call now to get more information!

About Royale Realtors India
Royale Realtors India is a luxury real estate company. We help High Networth Individuals, Top Industrialists, NRIs, MNCs, and Investors by offering Personalised Real Estate bouquet services in Prime Locations of SOUTH DELHI through Premium Luxury Listings of high-end Properties, like Villas, Land, Apartments, builder floors, flats, bungalows, duplexes, triplexes or Offices. Founded In 1990, We’ve spent decades excelling in the competitive landscape of South Delhi real estate, establishing a class reputation as expert advisors serving boutique-style solutions to a niche clientele. Our business is built on communication, dedication, and transparency. The processes we have mastered have helped us to rise to the level of the best real estate consultants In South Delhi. With our sharp knowledge of the local market, We’ve helped over 500 families & many multinational companies in South Delhi find their desired properties, and We are confident we can help you find yours too, or in your family or for your organization.

Our Serving Areas
Please feel free to contact us for sale, purchase, leasing, to-let, and collaborations.
